Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.events.vcevents

package it.polimi.ingsw.common.events.vcevents
Classes that implement the events from a view to the controller of the Masters of Renaissance game.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    VCEvent
    Events sent from View to Controller (client commands).
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ReqActivateProductions
    Client request for production activation.
    ReqBuyDevCard
    Client request to buy a development card.
    ReqChooseLeaders
    Client request for setup leader choice.
    ReqChooseResources
    Client request for setup resource choice.
    ReqEndTurn
    Client request to end the player's turn.
    ReqJoin
    Client request to connect to the server's lobby.
    ReqLeaderAction
    Leader action request.
    ReqNewGame
    Client request for a new game.
    ReqQuit
    Client request to disconnect from a game.
    ReqSwapShelves
    Client request to swap two shelves.
    ReqTakeFromMarket
    Client request to take resources from the market.
